$interpreted: Jerus: Fatima, we just received the news. Rune Academy will have someone come later today to negotiate with us and retrieve the students.
Fatima: Do we know who's coming?
Jerus: That we don't know. I suppos it's their teacher...don't you want to come and take a look?
Fatima: No thanks, if my other choice was to see those people's ugly mugs, I would much rather go on patrol!
Jerus: Where are you going for your patrol? Do you need someone to go with you?
Fatima: No need for that. I'm just going to take a quick look around the south hunting grounds. You guys can handle the negotiation.
Jerus: Understood. You be careful.
Fatima: ...It's supposed to be the growth period right now. Yet the fruits and plants in this area aren't growing at all...
Fatima: So the impact caused by the change in Soul Energy has spread to this area as well?
Fatima: These people from the Rune Academy...how much do they have to ruin our lives before they are satisfied!
Fatima: WHAT!?
Fatima: Guess I'll have to deal with you first!
Fatima: Whew~ Got caught a bit off guard back there...better return to the tribe soon...
Fatima: They're still coming!?
Fatima: Damnit...is this where it all ends...
Charle: Are you alright?
Fatima: A human?
Charle: Are you bleeding? Don't move. I'll treat your wounds!
Fatima: These are minor injuries. I don't need...
Fatima: What are you doing? Let go of me!
Fatima: Don't touch me so! What are you...
Fatima: The bleeding stopped...did you just use a Rune item?
Charle: Your wounds have not fully healed. Let me help you...
Fatima: No need. Just who exactly are you?
Charle: Oh, right. I haven't introduced myself yet. I'm Charle Ceres.
Fatima: Charle Ceres...Charle...?
Fatima: Headmaster of Rune Academy! Are you the one who's here to negotiate with us?
Charle: Yes. Our students made a mistake. Naturally, it's up to the headmaster to clean up their mess.
Charle: Only problem, as I was on my way to visit your people, I accidentally got lost...
Fatima: Got lost!?
Fatima: So someone like you is the headmaster of Rune Academy...unbelievable...
Charle: To be honest, I've heard things about pretty much all the leaders and captains for Panthers...you should be Miss Fatima, right?
Charle: Would you please take me to the Panther tribe? Or else, I have no idea how long it'll take me to reach there...
Fatima: Since we ran into each other, I can't just leave you here. Come with me. I'll take you to the tribe.
Charle: Thank you. Perfect, someone to chat with.
Fatima: I don't want to talk.
Charle: What do Panthers usually eat? I'm a pretty good cook. Maybe we can share some recipes so we can understand each other better?
Fatima: None of my business.
Charle: What do Panthers usually do for fun? In the Academy, at the end of each semester, we always...
Fatima: Another word from you and you'll finish this trip alone!
